        "fileKey": "scriptjs",
        "contents": "const spiralDiagonals = (n) => {\n  const Sn2 = (n) => {\n    return n*(n+1)*(2*n+1)/6;\n  };\n  const Sn = (n) => {\n    return n*(n+1)/2;\n  };\n  let sum = (Sn2(n-1) + Sn(n-1) + n-1) + (Math.floor(n/2) + Sn2(n));\n  return sum;\n};",
        "error": null,
        "seed": "const spiralDiagonals = (n) => {\n  const Sn2 = (n) => {\n    return n*(n+1)*(2*n+1)/6;\n  };\n  const Sn = (n) => {\n    return n*(n+1)/2;\n  };\n  let sum = (Sn2(n-1) + Sn(n-1) + n-1) + (Math.floor(n/2) + Sn2(n));\n  return sum;\n};"
